=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532245\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104szk1665702783628.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/szk1665702783628.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/szk1665702783628.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"szk1665702783628\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Uniface 10: Changes in the JavaScript API\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface JavaScript API has been enhanced with new and changed APIs.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">New APIs</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n API\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Change\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n Introduced\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"irg1665702783697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/irg1665702783697.html\" title=\"The uniface.ValidationError object provides access to the error number and message of a validation error on the server. It is returned by the FieldErrorContext.getError function when used in the showError and clearError web triggers.\">uniface.ValidationError</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n JavaScript object for accessing information about a server-side validation error\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.3.03\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbs1665702756289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbs1665702756289.html\" title=\"The uniface.FieldErrorContext object is the this object for the showError and clearError web triggers. It provides access to information about the field in error, the validation error, and the DOM node that represent the field in the layout.\">uniface.FieldErrorContext</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n JavaScript object for accessing information required in the showError and clearError web triggers\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.3.03\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xbg1665702534713.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xbg1665702534713.html\" title=\"The uniface.View object represents a view of a component that has been created by calling instance.createView().\">uniface.View</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n JavaScript object that represents a view (layout) of a DSP component instance. Provides functions for showing, hiding, and deleting views.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.02\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vzv1665702534087.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vzv1665702534087.html\" title=\"Creates a View of the component instance with the specified name and layout.\">createView</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Create a View object to represent a view of a DSP component instance.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.02\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xlf1665702534189.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xlf1665702534189.html\" title=\"Get the specified view of the component instance.\">getView()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Get the specified view of the component instance.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.02\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gjv1665702534276.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gjv1665702534276.html\" title=\"Returns an array of uniface.View objects representing the views of a component instance.\">getViews</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Returns an array of <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.View</span> objects representing the views of a component instance.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.02\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ule1665702755478.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ule1665702755478.html\" title=\"The uniface.datastore API provides access to the local browser-based database used for client-side data storage.\">uniface.datastore</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Provides create, update, retrieve, and delete access to browser-based databases.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fzt1665702534368.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fzt1665702534368.html\" title=\"Serialize the component data from the specified component instance into a string with JSON content.\">getData()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Serialize the component data from the specified component instance into a JSON stream.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qbf1665702534519.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbf1665702534519.html\" title=\"Load component data from a JSON stream into the specified uniface.Instance object.\">setData()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Load component data from a JSON stream into the specified component instance.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wfs1665702783767.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wfs1665702783767.html\" title=\"Gives focus to the HTML input widget of the field.\">focus()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Gives the field focus.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ctc1665702783835.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ctc1665702783835.html\" title=\"Returns true if the field's HTML input widget has focus.\">hasFocus()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Checks whether the field has focus.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dig1665702538574.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dig1665702538574.html\" title=\"Return a JavaScript object containing the field syntax properties as defined in the field's definition.\">getDeclarativeSyntax()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a JavaScript object containing the field syntax properties, as defined in the field's definition.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zkz1665702538660.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zkz1665702538660.html\" title=\"Returns an error object for the field, if a syntax error or validation error occurred.\">getError()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.SyntaxError</span> object for the field, if a syntax error occurred.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"psh1665702538803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/psh1665702538803.html\" title=\"The uniface.SyntaxError object provides access to the error number and message of a field syntax error, and to the incorrect field value that caused the error.\">uniface.SyntaxError</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n Error object returned by <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getError</span>, which contains the exceptionCode, error message, and valueInError.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"irg1665702535447.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/irg1665702535447.html\" title=\"The uniface.Label object provides access to selected properties of the label it represents. It is returned by the getLabel function of uniface.Occurrence and the uniface.Field objects.\">uniface.Label</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__2\">\n New <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Label</span> object. The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">setValue</span> and <span class=\"keyword apiname\">getValue</span> functions can be used to set and get the text of the label.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d71e1_d72e1_d73e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Changed APIs</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n API\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n Change\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n Introduced\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dtg1665702533539.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" title=\"The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.\">uniface.Instance</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n The following functions have been added:\n <ul class=\"sl simple\">\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">createView</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getView</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getViews()</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.02\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dlx1665702535259.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" title=\"The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.\">uniface.Field</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n The following functions have been added:\n <ul class=\"sl simple\">\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">focus()</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">hasFocus()</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getDeclarativeSyntax</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getError</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"sli\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getLabel</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tle1665702533236.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tle1665702533236.html\" title=\"Asynchronously activates an operation on the current component instance, or the main instance.\">activate()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a JavaScript Promise object.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dxn1665702533340.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dxn1665702533340.html\" title=\"Asynchronously creates a DSP component instance and executes the specified operation (if any).\">createInstance()</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n Returns a JavaScript Promise object.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hfh1665702535808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" title=\"The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.\">uniface.Occurrence</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__2\">\n The following functions have been added:\n <p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getLabel</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"szk1665702783628__table_d74e1_d75e1_d76e1__entry__3\">\n 10.2.01\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532245\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532245\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface 10: Changes in the JavaScript API Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface 10: Changes in the JavaScript API The Uniface JavaScript API has been enhanced with new and changed APIs. Table 1. New APIs API Change Introduced uniface.ValidationError JavaScript object for accessing information about a server-side validation error 10.3.03 uniface.FieldErrorContext JavaScript object for accessing information required in the showError and clearError web triggers 10.3.03 uniface.View JavaScript object that represents a view (layout) of a DSP component instance. Provides functions for showing, hiding, and deleting views. 10.2.02 createView Create a View object to represent a view of a DSP component instance. 10.2.02 getView() Get the specified view of the component instance. 10.2.02 getViews Returns an array of uniface.View objects representing the views of a component instance. 10.2.02 uniface.datastore Provides create, update, retrieve, and delete access to browser-based databases. 10.2.01 getData() Serialize the component data from the specified component instance into a JSON stream. 10.2.01 setData() Load component data from a JSON stream into the specified component instance. 10.2.01 focus() Gives the field focus. 10.2.01 hasFocus() Checks whether the field has focus. 10.2.01 getDeclarativeSyntax() Returns a JavaScript object containing the field syntax properties, as defined in the field's definition. 10.2.01 getError() Returns a uniface.SyntaxError object for the field, if a syntax error occurred. 10.2.01 uniface.SyntaxError Error object returned by getError , which contains the exceptionCode, error message, and valueInError. 10.2.01 uniface.Label New uniface.Label object. The setValue and getValue functions can be used to set and get the text of the label. 10.2.01 Table 2. Changed APIs API Change Introduced uniface.Instance The following functions have been added: createView getView getViews() 10.2.02 uniface.Field The following functions have been added: focus() hasFocus() getDeclarativeSyntax getError getLabel 10.2.01 activate() Returns a JavaScript Promise object. 10.2.01 createInstance() Returns a JavaScript Promise object. 10.2.01 uniface.Occurrence The following functions have been added: getLabel 10.2.01 Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}